# Welcome to my personal page

I am not good at updating this site, so expect stale content.
I started my PhD in Computer Science at the [University of Cambridge](http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk) after having finished my Undergraduate at the same place. Currently I am a co-founder at [aircloak](http://aircloak.com), and very excited about what the future has in store for us there!

You can reach me at these other locations:

- Github under @sebastian
- Twitter as [@probst](http://twitter.com/probst)
- Facebook (if I know you) http://facebook.com/sebastianprobsteide
- [About.me](http://about.me/sebastianprobsteide)

Thanks for stopping by.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
